# Pentagon model refresh - 2026-05-22

## Default model

Before repair:

- defaults read run.pentagon.app pentagon.defaultModel -> claude-opus-4-7[1m]

Repair command:

- defaults write run.pentagon.app pentagon.defaultModel -string gpt-5.5

After repair:

- defaults read run.pentagon.app pentagon.defaultModel -> gpt-5.5

## Recheck - 2026-05-22T21:54Z

The default drifted again after the earlier repair:

- before: defaults read run.pentagon.app pentagon.defaultModel -> claude-opus-4-7[1m]
- repair: defaults write run.pentagon.app pentagon.defaultModel -string gpt-5.5
- after: defaults read run.pentagon.app pentagon.defaultModel -> gpt-5.5

This means the default model setting is repairable but not durable yet. Treat
model readiness as amber until a fresh Pentagon launch plus live per-agent
readback proves every active agent is still on gpt-5.5.

